data.description:
Miami’s 5-Star Boutique Yacht Charter Operator Since 2000

Miami Boat Charters Boutique Service is Always Open. Simply Call During Business Hours or Use Our Live Chat Website Feature 24/7/365.

Our helpful staff are at your service day and night ready to delight from booking to boarding.

Miami Boat Charters offers the largest and newest selection of fully crewed Boat Charters, Luxury Yacht Rentals and Part Boats in Miami Beach. We specialize in private, corporate and special occasion charters departing from select Miami Marinas. Most vessels accommodate groups of up to 12 guests on Day Charters, 10 guests for Term Charters and up to 320 guests on our Party Boats.
